## 2. Functional Requirements

### FR-AUTH: Authentication & Authorization

| ID | Requirement | Priority |
|----|-------------|---------|
| FR-AUTH-01 | System shall allow users to register with email and password | Must |
| FR-AUTH-02 | System shall authenticate users via JWT (15-min access token) | Must |
| FR-AUTH-03 | System shall issue refresh tokens (7-day expiry, rotating) | Must |
| FR-AUTH-04 | System shall assign user roles: Student, Engineer, Architect, Company, Admin | Must |
| FR-AUTH-05 | System shall restrict features based on role (see BR-02) | Must |
| FR-AUTH-06 | System shall support password reset via email | Should |
| FR-AUTH-07 | System shall support Google OAuth login | Could |

