## 4. Constraints

- **Timeline**: 4 months, 2 developers
- **Budget**: Assumes Claude API costs, managed PostgreSQL, basic cloud hosting
- **Browser support**: Chrome 120+, Firefox 120+, Edge 120+ (no IE, no mobile MVP)
- **AI Provider**: Claude API primary; OpenAI as fallback; Ollama for local dev
- **No real-time multi-user editing in MVP** (Phase 4 feature)

---

## 5. Assumptions

- Users have stable internet connection (WebSocket-dependent features)
- LLM API is available and within cost budget
- Python simulation service runs separately and is always up (or gracefully degraded)
- All users access via modern desktop browser